name: Nifty Thrifty Ticket
description:
This ticket is good for 1 NFT

Redeemable at the Thrifty Store 

niftythrifty.io 

Obtain a Thrifty Ticket by donating your old, stale, or unwanted NFTs. Or to simply trade into something better. 

Qualifying submissions: 
1. A past sale over 1 Tez 
2. No illicit content or copymints

Donated items that do not qualify will not be eligible for a Thrifty Ticket.

You can resell this ticket.
